 DemoNuGrid connected;values;F;colTitles;rowTitles;cellWidths;cellTypes
 EWC.CONNECTED‚Üêconnected
 ‚éïPW‚Üê1000

‚çù NuGrid Demo - Phase 7: Component Embedding
‚çù This demo shows NuGrid with embedded EWC components (Edit, Button, Combo, Label)

 F‚Üê'F1'
 F eWC'Form' 'NuGrid Demo - Component Embedding'(50 50)(550 650)('Coord' 'Pixel')

‚çù Create sample data: 6 rows √ó 5 columns
‚çù Columns: Product (Edit), Quantity (Numeric), In Stock (Checkbox), Color (Combo), Price (Label)
 values‚Üê6 5‚ç¥‚ç¨
 values[1;]‚Üê'Apple' 150 1 'Red' 2.99
 values[2;]‚Üê'Banana' 250 1 'Yellow' 1.49
 values[3;]‚Üê'Cherry' 50 0 'Red' 5.99
 values[4;]‚Üê'Date' 75 1 'Brown' 4.49
 values[5;]‚Üê'Elderberry' 30 0 'Purple' 8.99
 values[6;]‚Üê'Fig' 100 1 'Brown' 3.49

‚çù Column headers
 colTitles‚Üê'Product' 'Quantity' 'In Stock' 'Color' 'Price $'

‚çù Row headers (row numbers 1-6)
 rowTitles‚Üê‚ç≥6

‚çù Column widths: Product=100, Quantity=80, InStock=70, Color=90, Price=70
 cellWidths‚Üê100 80 70 90 70

‚çù Create the NuGrid component
 (F,'.G')eWC'NuGrid'('Posn'(100 20))('Size'(220 440))('Values' values)('ColTitles' colTitles)('RowTitles' rowTitles)('CellWidths' cellWidths)('TitleWidth' 40)('CurCell'(1 1))('VScroll' ¬Ø1)

‚çù Create Input components (children of the grid) - these are templates for cell types
‚çù 1: Edit for text (Product name)
 (F,'.G.E1')eWC'Edit'

‚çù 2: Numeric Edit for numbers (Quantity)
 (F,'.G.E2')eWC'Edit'('FieldType' 'Numeric')

‚çù 3: Checkbox for boolean (In Stock)
 (F,'.G.B1')eWC'Button'('Style' 'Check')('Caption' '')

‚çù 4: Combo for dropdown (Color)
 (F,'.G.C1')eWC'Combo'('Items'('Red' 'Yellow' 'Green' 'Brown' 'Purple' 'Orange'))

‚çù 5: Label for read-only display (Price)
 (F,'.G.L1')eWC'Label'

‚çù Set up Input array (component IDs) and CellTypes matrix
‚çù Input: array of component IDs that can be used in cells
 (F,'.G')eWS'Input'((F,'.G.E1')(F,'.G.E2')(F,'.G.B1')(F,'.G.C1')(F,'.G.L1'))

‚çù CellTypes: matrix of 1-based indices into Input array
‚çù Each column uses a different component type
 cellTypes‚Üê6 5‚ç¥1 2 3 4 5  ‚çù All rows use: Col1=Edit, Col2=Numeric, Col3=Check, Col4=Combo, Col5=Label
 (F,'.G')eWS'CellTypes' cellTypes

‚çù Add event handlers
 (F,'.G')eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'CellMove' 'CBNuGrid')
 (F,'.G')eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'CellChanged' 'CBNuGrid')
 (F,'.G')eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'KeyPress' 'CBNuGrid')

‚çù Add instruction labels
 (F,'.Info1')eWC'Label' 'Phase 7: Component Embedding Demo'(20 20)(20 600)
 (F,'.Info2')eWC'Label' 'Edit text in Product, numbers in Quantity, toggle checkboxes, select from dropdowns'(40 20)(20 600)
 (F,'.Info3')eWC'Label' 'Price column is read-only (Label). CellChanged event fires on edits.'(60 20)(20 600)

‚çù Event log section
 (F,'.LogTitle')eWC'Label' 'Event Log:'(340 20)(20 100)
 (F,'.Log')eWC'Label' '(Events will appear here)'(360 20)(160 600)
